I have a strange behavior (bug?) using valueSeq() after the 15.4.0 update. React is iterating twice my Immutable.Map. Whereas it's only iterating once when using toArray().

Here is my testing code :
```
render() {
  const myMap = Immutable.Map({a: 1, b: 2, c: 3})
  i = 0
  return (
    <div>
      { myMap.valueSeq().map( item => {
         console.log(i)  // logs 0 1 2 3 4 5
         i++    
         return <div key= {item}>{item}</div>
      }
      { myMap.toArray().map( item => {
         console.log(i)  // logs 0 1 2
         i++    
         return <div key= {item}>{item}</div>
      }
    </div>
)
}
```
Does anyone have the same behavior ?
